  • Field Details

    • namespacedKey

      protected final NamespacedKey namespacedKey
      The key that represents the name of this StructureType in its namespace.

      The namespace is the name of the plugin that owns this StructureType and the key is the simple name of the StructureType.

    • version

      protected final int version
      Gets the version of this StructureType. Note that changing the version creates a whole new StructureType and you'll have to take care of the transition.

  • Constructor Details

    • StructureType

      protected StructureType(NamespacedKey namespacedKey, int version, List<MovementDirection> validMovementDirections, List<Property<?>> supportedProperties, String localizationKey)
      Constructs a new StructureType. Don't forget to also register it using StructureTypeManager.register(StructureType).
      Parameters:
      namespacedKey - The key that represents the name of this StructureType in its namespace.

      The namespace is the name of the plugin that owns this StructureType and the key is the simple name of the StructureType.

      E.g.: "animatedarchitecture:windmill" or "animatedarchitecture:bigdoor".

      version - The version of this StructureType.

      This is used for serialization purposes. If you change the structure in a way that makes it incompatible with the previous version, you should increase this number. This will allow you to handle the transition between the old and new version.

      validMovementDirections - The valid movement directions for this structure.
      supportedProperties - The properties that are supported by this type.
      localizationKey - The key that is used to localize the name of this StructureType. For example, "structure.type.revolving_door".

    • StructureType

      protected StructureType(String pluginName, String simpleName, int version, List<MovementDirection> validMovementDirections, List<Property<?>> supportedProperties, String localizationKey)
      Constructs a new StructureType. Don't forget to also register it using StructureTypeManager.register(StructureType).
      Parameters:
      pluginName - The name of the plugin that owns this StructureType.

      The name can only contain (lowercase) letters, numbers, and underscores. Upper case letters will be converted to lowercase.

      simpleName - The simple name of this StructureType.

      The name can only contain (lowercase) letters, numbers, and underscores. Upper case letters will be converted to lowercase.

      The simple name is the name of the StructureType without the plugin name. For example, "windmill", "bigdoor", "flag", etc.

      version - The version of this StructureType.

      This is used for serialization purposes. If you change the structure in a way that makes it incompatible with the previous version, you should increase this number. This will allow you to handle the transition between the old and new version.

      validMovementDirections - The valid movement directions for this structure.
      supportedProperties - The properties that are supported by this type.
      localizationKey - The key that is used to localize the name of this StructureType. For example, "structure.type.revolving_door".

    • getFullKey

      public final String getFullKey()
      Gets the full name of the StructureType.

      This is the fully qualified name of the StructureType and includes the plugin name. For example, "animatedarchitecture:windmill", "animatedarchitecture:bigdoor", "animatedarchitecture:flag", etc.

      This is a shortcut for getNamespacedKey().getFullKey().

      Specified by:
      getFullKey in interface IKeyed
      Returns:
      The full name of the StructureType.
